data.description: Located in the Heart of Mossy Oaks and walking distance to the Spanish Moss Trail, this renovated 3 bedroom and 2 bath home features a massive fireplace & surround. Recently renovated w/new floors, brand new kitchen including granite counters. This was all done about four/five years ago. The owner took it a step further & put a new HVAC system in and reworked the entryway and primary suite! The main bedroom is a sanctuary with an amazing bathroom. The second bedroom is huge and has a ton of closet space.  Bedroom number 3 is a good third bedroom or big office. The large living area overlooks the huge back yard that borders a quiet duck pond.
